## External programs
browser firefox
pager   less
player  mplayer
notify-program notify-send

## Behaviour
auto-reload            yes
mark-as-read-on-hover  no
show-read-articles     yes

## Podcasts
download-path ~/Podcasts
max-downloads 2
podcast-auto-enqueue yes

## Notifications
notify-always yes
notify-format "%n unread, %d new"

## vi
unbind-key j
unbind-key k
bind-key j down
bind-key k up

## Colors
color info white blue bold
color listfocus black yellow
color listnormal black white
color background white white
